      .jumbotron
        p.lead
          | TweetPNG.com provides a super-simple API to display your latest tweet as an image.
      .row.marketing
        h2 How to do it...
        h3 Getting your latest tweet.
        p
          | Add&nbsp;
          code http://www.tweetpng.com/:username/tweet/latest.png
          | &nbsp;to your&nbsp;
          code img
          | &nbsp;tag in your HTML, where&nbsp;
          code :username
          | &nbsp;is your twitter username.
        p
          | Example:
        p.text-center
          img(src='/joshfinnie/tweet/last.png', alt='')
        h3 Getting a specific tweet
        p
          | Add&nbsp;
          code http://www.tweetpng.com/:username/tweet/:tweetID.png
          | &nbsp;to your&nbsp;
          code img
          | &nbsp;tag in your HTML, where&nbsp;
          code :username
          | &nbsp;is your twitter username.&nbsp;
          code :tweetID
          | &nbsp;is the Twitter ID of the tweet you want to use.
        p
          | Example:
        p.text-center
          img(src='/joshfinnie/tweet/354761173800976384.png', alt='')
